public static enum Types.DeviceStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<Types.DeviceStatus>

Defines the possible statuses a device can have. Available values are ONLINE, OFFLINE, PLAYING, TRANSITIONING, PAUSED_PLAYBACK, LOADED_MEDIA_INFO, STOPPED
